        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "Do you think this would be solved by automatically closing the window when the user moves away from it? That's what used to happen until close before merging #27855. I removed it on a whim when adding a mapping to close the window, thinking it would strengthen the promise of it being a regular window. But yes it still isn't, and I think it doesn't need to be (mainly to allow us to avoid the window from altering the layout of other windows, one of the advantages the message grid was originally added for). So I'm inclined to add that back, not sure how useful it is to keep the window open after moving away from it.",
